Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So... what do you think of my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty disgusting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty sad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I was trying to ruin Iona, but\Nit looks like my face was ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried to stop her from being a model, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...instead, it looks like\NI can't be a model anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Laughable, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:51.18,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:53.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:58.35,Main,,0,0,0,,The super cute Aki-lucky's\Nface looks like this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, take a look! Sad, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Quit it, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:08.15,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm stuck with this face now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:19.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You... and you... and Iona...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna decorate all of\Nyour faces, just like mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:24.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you girls doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.63,0:01:27.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You girls, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:50.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.20,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing good about this... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:56.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}said is right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my fault that Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't have a wish...\Nyou should quit while you're ahead, Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:14.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Quit. If something happens to you,\Nyour grandma is going to be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not the only one who should quit.\NYou should too, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:21.18,Main,,0,0,0,,If you lose, your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right... Kazuki-{\i1}kun {\i0}would suffer too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You saw what happened to Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't become like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No... Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko... I'm sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I can't quit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,A dream that would never come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I can already see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:56.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's... not be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:00.35,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.52,Main,,0,0,0,,...all the sad memories are\Ngoing to make you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, Yuzuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It was really fun being with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll treasure my matching scrunchie forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,The next time we meet, I'll be a new me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, as Kazuki's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:54.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:59.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:21.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:26.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:47.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru? Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Where in the world have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.84,Main,,0,0,0,,If you were going to be this late,\Nat least leave a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure... maybe I shouldn't be so concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...don't do anything to make Grandma worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:01.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Grandma home...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hurry up and go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Coldy-coldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just making some warm sweet {\i1}sake{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured Ru-{\i1}chan {\i0}would get home all cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:40.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you asking me\Nany questions, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:52.95,Main,,0,0,0,,When Ru-{\i1}chan {\i0}wants to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.87,Main,,0,0,0,,...then we can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:09.51,Main,,0,0,0,,"RUKO"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Did the sweet {\i1}sake {\i0}taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama likes Ru having fun with battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Seeing Ru sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,...I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, you made that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:51.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Guess it turns out I {\i1}can {\i0}make this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's some soup too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yesterday night, you just came home\Nand went straight to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I was worried there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Girls have days like that. Remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,This tastes good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,The last time you made French toast,\Nit wasn't cooked well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... I try to rush things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I kind of lose my cool a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down, and wait for the right timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:37.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Set my sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I don't lose\Nmy way, things will go fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Going out with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I'll be back quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.53,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make dinner tonight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:58.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What would be good? We had\NFrench toast this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,--Curry udon.\N--Curry udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I know everything about you, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:29.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:30.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't end up like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,"Card Shop ACE A"\N"Dueling Space Available"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"Dueling Tables"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,"GUEST BOOK"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.61,Main,,0,0,0,,"Would you like to have a battle on Sunday?\NI will be wearing a red scrunchie in my hair."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:24.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Trying to look for opponents like that\Nis a bit dangerous, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it, but the other\NSelectors may get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Even my LRIG is questioning what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:33.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"No Entry" "Construction Workers Only"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,"No Entry" "Construction Workers Only"\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Fighting aimlessly isn't really my style.\NI want to get this done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,With this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'll make my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You're pretty confident, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.65,Main,,0,0,0,,--Open!\N--Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm probably going first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:14.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Things feel different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I see where her confidence is coming from...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I was wrong all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,People made me think I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.40,Main,,0,0,0,,A love that isn't forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:41.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, I felt bad seeing\NKazuki-{\i1}kun {\i0}stalked by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.41,Main,,0,0,0,,A feeling that isn't forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That's super erotic! That's super pervy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Spell, Splitting Conviction!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Direct damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll reverse everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll reverse everything of this world\Nwhere my feelings aren't forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:13.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be by Kazuki's side!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Dang, I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so good, Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, can you look at my deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're going to use Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup. Because the gem-themed SIGNI is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki uses Red too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a little thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, is it okay if I bring juice in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:55.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}... can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, the vending machine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:14.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to be so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:20.42,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I really want to share\Nmy feelings with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,...want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:30.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm not really into things like that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there someone else you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It isn't because... of Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You're always with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:50.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped if\Neveryone suspected you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?!\NWhat do you mean by "suspected"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, the two of you\Nare doing it and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone's saying stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's "everyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's saying stuff like that? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel sorry for Yuzuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me! Who said that?\NMatsumoto-{\i1}san{\i0}? Senda-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go and correct whoever it is! Now, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:21.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You're always so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess that's how angry you get\Nwhen it has to do with Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if I'm wrong then prove it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Prove...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Kiss me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to kiss you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You can at least kiss me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.92,Main,,0,0,0,,If you can't, then that means\Nyou must love Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Wait, Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It is different than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon, Canon! With its effect, banish Hass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel a burning sensation inside of me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...the very core of my body is surprisingly cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Really... with this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:14.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, I'll ask you again... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:18.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,If you win this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,...your wish that you've\Nheld dear will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:35.39,Main,,0,0,0,,When I saw what happened\Nto Hitoe... I blamed you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I was told the truth\Nfrom the very beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...I would still have wanted my wish granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:47.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I would have chosen my path to battle,\Nto become an Eternal Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Go! Eagle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Right... Even if I was scared,\NI would have decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:59.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel really sorry for Hitoe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:04.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe's wish was something which\Ncould come true without being a Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...is something that would never come true,\Neven if the world was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish that needed to rely\Non battles as a Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Your final attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:20.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...your final call. Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, together with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I... accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.42,Main,,0,0,0,,And...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:46.26,Main,,0,0,0,,--...now, a new Eternal Girl will be born!\N--...now, a new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,--Adamasphere!\N--Adamasphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It's happening...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the birth... of an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha...na...yo...{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your precious day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't\Nwant to go out and play?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Being with Grandma is really calming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if battling is fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...I shouldn't go near it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.78,Main,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's... not be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:01.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Sorry. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I... shouldn't go near anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing,\Nleaving like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Honoka-{\i1}chan {\i0}is real angry, saying that\Nyou did something horrible to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize with you, so come back right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:26.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Girls are terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Totally different from Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki is always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:34.99,Main,,0,0,0,,She's honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:39.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if things are rough...\Nshe tries to keep it to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, the two of you\Nare doing it and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I just got dizzy there for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll get the food...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You better lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you able to walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you put something on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:24.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Something smells pleasant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:33.09,Main,,0,0,0,,They say that if you\Nthink someone smells good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.59,Main,,0,0,0,,...the genes are attracted to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:41.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Your person of fate... smells pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard about that before too,\Nbut you got that wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,The genes are attracted to a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.94,Main,,0,0,0,,We're twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe we were born with differences\Nthat were split between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We're finally one like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:08.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What's not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You... and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Did something happen with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to talk about anything with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm... always on your side, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Forever, yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe? Did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You haven't even eaten lunch, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:04.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I have something good for you. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, you liked this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,There was an ad that said a new WIXOSS deck\Ncame out, so I went and bought one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.77,Main,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, take a look at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I also bought a cake too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'd like something sweet instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nodding to the clockwork shadow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}opens the door to the end,{\i0}\N{\i1}bringing in the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There we catch glimpses of the perilous answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's prayer becomes taboo tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upside-down maze reflects{\i0}\N{\i1}the heavens and the earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gear begins to turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully among the masses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that bell resounding in{\i0}\N{\i1}the skies beckons the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward even beyond eternity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is the future I chose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unreachable summer clouds{\i0}\N{\i1}and flickering heat haze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day I'll get back my place of smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,A card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,The card did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you spread it to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.92,0:23:40.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks... Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:47.05,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Cruel Truth."
